dline-alongside-cmat-english-teacher-daniel-avery-and-more-buy-tickets-3809677">音乐节组织者宣布</a>，继爱尔兰说唱三人组广受好评的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kneecap-fine-art-album-review-3765120">《Fine Art》</a> （2024 年）之后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a>将成为明年的头条新闻。</p><p>之前确认的其他乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">CMAT</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/english-teacher">English Teacher</a> （今年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/english-teacher-win-the-2024-mercury-prize-for-this-could-be-texas-3791098">水星奖获得者</a>）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daniel-avery">Daniel Avery</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mannequin-pussy">Mannequin Pussy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/psychedelic-porn-crumpets">Psychedelic Porn Crumpets</a> 、Puzzle（首次在英国音乐节亮相）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sprints">Sprints</a> 。</p><p>再往下是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/erol-alkan">Erol Alkan</a> BTB Optimo (Espacio)、Frankie &amp; The Witch Fingers、Gaye Su Akyol、Getdown Services、Hello Mary、HiTech、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-radar/jasmine-4-t-announces-debut-album-you-are-the-morning-shares-moving-new-single-elephant-3805502">Jasmine.4.t</a> 、Martin Rev、Mermaid Chunky、Patriarchy、Ugly、WITCH 和 Wine嘴唇。</p><p>现在，Wide Awake 公布了更多 2025 年艺术家名单，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/marie-davidson">Marie Davidson</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nadine-shah">Nadine Shah</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/warmduscher">Warmduscher</a> 。</p><p>在其他地方，最近登上<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/fcukers-19-08-2024-3784706"><em>NME</em>封面的明星</a>Fcukers、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cobrah">COBRAH</a> 、Chanel Beads 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gurriers">Gurriers</a>也将登台表演。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DC6aOVfN8Zy/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#