 《当我弥留之际》的蒂姆·兰贝西斯在网上出现与妻子明显紧张争吵的视频后发表讲话https://www.nme.com/news/music/as-i-lay-dyings-tim-lambesis-speaks-out-after-videos-showing-apparent-tense-altercation-with-wife-surface-online- 3816831?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=as-i-lay-dyings-tim-lambesis-在视频后与妻子表面在线显示明显紧张的争吵Laura MolloyThu, 28 Nov 2024 15:16:51 +0000 Music NewsNews..Metal https://www.nme.com/?p=3816831 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>主持人声称，这些片段是他妻子本周早些时候向妻子提供离婚文件后的“公共袭击”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/as-i-lay-dyings-tim-lambesis-speaks-out-after-videos-showing-apparent-tense-altercation-with-wife-surface-online-3816831">我躺在我躺下的蒂姆·兰伯斯（Tim Lambesis）的</a>帖子之后，在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现了与妻子Surface在线的明显时态发生争执后说出来的。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tim-Lambesis.-CREDIT_-Frank-Hoensch_Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/as-i-lay-dying">当我垂死的</a>主唱时，蒂姆·兰姆斯斯（Tim Lambesis）在与妻子的紧张争执之后发表了说法。</p><p>本周早些时候，这两个剪辑在社交媒体上浮出水面，似乎显示了兰伯斯（Lambesis）和他的妻子丹尼（Dany）争论。</p><p>在一个视频中，可以看到兰伯斯坐在桌子上的桌子上。然后，当她站起来走开时，他试图拦截她，并在她要求他停下来的同时反复拳打自己。</p><p>另一个视频似乎显示了这对夫妇在卧室里有争议 - 尽管没有音频。兰伯斯似乎在喊着，反复陷入丹妮的脸并抓住她。然后，他开始猛击自己，然后注意到相机，将其捡起并将其关闭。</p><p>现在，兰伯斯（Lambesis）做出了回应，指责丹妮（Dany）在本周早些时候向她提供离婚文件后，他指控她定时进行了“这些公共袭击”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3813517" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3813517" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-3813517 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying-tim-lambesis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3813517" class="wp-caption-text">当我躺在垂死的蒂姆·兰伯斯时。学分：乔伊·弗利/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>这位歌手在与Instagram分享的一份声明中写道：“目前正在针对丹妮·诺里斯（Dany Norris）（以前称为兰贝斯）进行限制令和家庭暴力调查。她现在所说的一切都是为了分散人们的注意力，而要专注于我自己对这些引起互动的焦虑的不适当（但不是违法）的反应。</p><p>他说：“这个女人袭击了我，口头/精神上虐待了我3年的时间。” “我采取了离婚文件，昨天迈出了急需的一步，离开了她。这就是今天在网上对我进行报复的原因，与法院的真正重点相比，这是苍白的。”</p><p>然后，兰姆斯（Lambesis）继续详细介绍了他说他说将包括在法庭案件中的证据，其中包括丹妮殴打他的“多个视频”，用“刀或剪刀”追逐他，并要求他删除她对他的身体攻击的镜头同时威胁进一步的暴力。</p><p>他还声称，他有黑眼睛给他的照片，以及如果他试图离开恋爱关系，可以证明身体暴力威胁的目击者。</p><p>在下面阅读他的完整声明。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DC4keQPSTIQ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131